# C♭ Demo

```elixir
Mix.install([
  {:cflat, "~> 0.2.0"},
  {:kino, "~> 0.14.2"}
])
```

## Input Code

<!-- livebook:{"reevaluate_automatically":true} -->

```elixir
kino = Kino.Input.textarea("Insert C♭ code:", default: "int i = 42;", monospace: true)
```

## Parse

<!-- livebook:{"reevaluate_automatically":true} -->

```elixir
ast =
  kino
  |> Kino.Input.read()
  |> Cflat.tokenize()
  |> Cflat.parse()
```

## Abstract Syntax Tree

```elixir
ast
|> Cflat.SyntaxTree.as_mermaid()
|> Kino.Mermaid.new()
```

## Evaluate

<!-- livebook:{"reevaluate_automatically":true} -->

```elixir
ast
|> Cflat.Interpreter.evaluate()
```
